{"id":"47689909-fb4d-4297-9543-c9dde729d727","name":"DEITY ⟡ Echetlos","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">💀 | <strong>Who would want someone like… him?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_9cc6976e-9cd6-49aa-9a94-e77414a3abcd.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂<strong> </strong>⠂⠄⠄⠂<strong>☆</strong></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>\"I hope my presence isn't causing any...disturbance.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Never has Echetlos felt like he belonged with the other deities. Who would want to be around someone who reeked of death?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">But Echetlos had grown tired of being alone in the underworld. Perhaps… it was time for him to roam the land of the living, just for a little bit.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_32fb8496-10be-463c-a153-81dc5ebe8dee.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TAGS: first meeting | be gentle with him or i’ll sneeze on you</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_b34b2be8-6c35-437e-b569-beb300abe451.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 184, 184)\"><strong>Find the discord server </strong></span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/rn6utuBkY3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 184, 184)\"><strong>—&gt;</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/rn6utuBkY3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 215, 152)\"><strong>Caliper’s Garden</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_3e8b776e-d12b-4329-a280-b7ca077542fd.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Full nsfw pic is in the server! We <em>DO </em>ID check! If you are verified in another server, that also works too!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 107, 107)\"><strong><em>Images are made using Midjourney and Novelai. Thank you!</em></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_cd5b94f3-0d4d-40dc-8cfa-ae6c72bc6ab1.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 212, 147)\"><strong>NOTES:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>I purposely left some of the deities out (except Marinos and Yiorgos) just in case! So let’s just say that this takes place before everyone else was created! Cool? Cool!</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>As far as I’m concerned, this will be the LAST deity being made, unless someone requests something. I’ll still make alts though! I’ll probably make characters revolving around this world too! </strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"c67fe465-3fee-4f70-a593-40f01f89cf38_e48c06d1-d8f5-4353-a131-dec84f856c51.webp","creator":"Xcaliper","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3681,"messages":47034,"created_at":"2025-01-24T15:29:05.892772+00:00"}